node.title: Teenager missing after attack authorities believe involved two sharks at Port Beach
node.alt: A line of search boats in the water at Port Beach.
node.description: Water police and rescue helicopters are searching for a teenagerÂ after a shark attack off Port Beach in Fremantle.
node.content:
["Water police and rescue helicopters are searching for a teenager after a shark attack off Port Beach in Fremantle.", "It is believed the male teenager was swimming\u00a0next to a dinghy at the time.", "Authorities believe he was attacked by two sharks, a great white and a tiger.", "Swimmers and witnesses at the scene are visibly shocked.", "At least five\u00a0Water Police and Sea Rescue boats and two helicopters are scouring the area and an ambulance has been sent to the scene.", "", "
Police rescue boats searched the area for a person feared taken by a shark.(ABC News: David Weber)
", "Beaches from Leighton to South Beach have been closed.", "
Leeman shark attack victim shocked
", "Witness Alex Dodds, who was at Port Beach this morning, said he was shocked to find out about the incident.", "\"Apparently they're looking for a body, so sounds pretty bad. Hopefully they can find it,\" he said.", "\"I was coming down for my first swim post-op, six weeks ago. First time back in the ocean after my [shark] attack, so pretty heavy.", "\"I was attacked up in Leeman in June by a big great white, so it's close to home.", "\"I just feel so bad, obviously, for the bloke and then the family as well, it's just so sad.\"", "More to come."]
